NG0604:3: dpal rdo rje khro bo chen po rta mgrin zhes bya ba'i rgyud kyi rgyal po //
NG0604:4: byang chub sems dpa' 'phags pa spyan ras gzigs dbang phyug thugs rje chen po la phyag 'tshal lo //
NG0604:5: 'di skad bdag gis thos pa'i dus gcig na //
NG0604:6: 'og min chos kyi dbyings pad+ma dbang gi pho brang na //
NG0604:7: rgya chad phyogs mtshams med pa rin po che 'od kyi pho brang na //
NG0604:8: bcom ldan 'das dpal pad+ma dbang chen gzi brjid 'bar ba zhes bya ba la //
NG0604:9: de bzhin gshegs pa rnams dang thabs cig pa 'di lta ste //
NG0604:10: de bzhin gshegs pa gsung rdo rje dang *//

NG0604:21: gnyis su med pa shes rab kyi yum dang thabs

NG0604:23: byed dang *// lha ma yin thar byed dang *//
NG0604:28: dmyal ba thar byed rnams dang thabs gcig go / yang khyad par gyi 'khor //
NG0604:29: byang chub sems dpa' spyan ras gzigs thugs rje chen
NG0604:30: po yab yum sras dang bcas pa dang thabs gcig
NG0604:31: tu bzhugs so // yang ngo bo nyid kyi 'khor //
NG0604:33: don gcig pa zhes bya ba'i 'khor dang *//
NG0604:36: nyid las mi zhan pa dang *//
NG0604:38: ma bkag rang gsal zhes bya ba dang *//
NG0604:39: ma btus khyab rdal zhes bya ba dang thabs gcig tu bzhugs so //
NG0604:40: de nas yang bcom ldan 'das pad+ma dbang chen gyis //
NG0604:41: dregs pa tshar gcod pa zhes bya ba'i ting nge 'dzin la snyoms par zhugs so //
NG0604:42: ting nge 'dzin la snyoms par zhugs pa'i tshe //
NG0604:43: 'khor rnams kyang ting nge 'dzin la snyoms par zhugs so //
NG0604:44: de'i tshe ting nge 'dzin du ma 'khor rnams kyi rgyud la 'di lta ste //
NG0604:45: skye ba med pa zhes bya ba'i ting nge 'dzin dang *//
NG0604:46: 'gag pa med pa zhes bya ba'i ting nge 'dzin dang *//
NG0604:47: gnas pa med pa zhes bya ba'i ting nge 'dzin dang *//
NG0604:48: spros pa dang bral ba zhes bya ba'i ting nge 'dzin dang *//
NG0604:49: brjod pa dang bral ba zhes bya ba'i ting nge 'dzin dang *//
NG0604:50: rdo rje lta bu zhes bya ba'i ting nge 'dzin dang *//
NG0604:51: dregs pa tshar gcod pa bdud 'dul ba zhes bya ba'i ting nge 'dzin rgyud la skyes so //
NG0604:52: de'i tshe de'i dus na byang chub sems dpa' spyan
NG0604:53: ras gzigs kyis bdud dang log 'dren thams cad 'dul
NG0604:54: ba'i ting nge 'dzin la snyoms par zhugs nas //
NG0604:55: thugs zhi ba'i ngang las ma g.yos par //
NG0604:56: sku khro bo rta mgrin gyi gzugs su yang dag par ston par gyur to //
NG0604:57: spyi gtsug rta mgo ljang khur rta skad thengs gsum ston pas //
NG0604:59: srid gsum zil gyis mnan nas bdud dang dregs pa thams cad tshar bcad de //
NG0604:60: 'khor thams cad bka' bzhin byed par gyur to //
NG0604:61: rta mgrin dregs pa tshar gcod kyi rgyud las //
NG0604:62: gleng gzhi'i le'u ste dang po'o // // de nas
NG0604:63: 'khor gyi nang nas gsungs rdo rje zhes bya ba
NG0604:64: 'khor gyi gtso bar gyur pa de stan las langs
NG0604:65: te // bcom ldan 'das pa pad+ma dbang chen la
NG0604:66: phyag 'tshal bskor ba byas nas 'di skad ces gsol
NG0604:67: te // to // e ma ho bcom ldan dbang chen rgyal //
NG0604:68: thugs rje'i bdag po spyan ras gzigs //
NG0604:69: rta mchog rgyal por sku khros nas //
NG0604:70: bdud dang bgegs rnams tshar bcad phyir //
NG0604:71: nyid kyis lta sgom spyod 'bras dang *//
NG0604:72: bsnyen sgrub las la sbyar ba dang *//
NG0604:73: dbang dang sbyin sreg mnan dang bsrung *//
NG0604:75: bstod bskul 'phrin las rta bro dang *//
NG0604:76: dgra bgegs gdug pa tshar gcad pa'i //
NG0604:77: las kyi rim pa ma lus pa //
NG0604:78: dbang chen rgyal pos bshad du gsol //
NG0604:79: zhes gsol nas ched du gleng @#//
NG0604:81: rta mgrin dregs pa tshar gcod kyi rgyud las //
NG0604:82: gleng bslang bstan pa'i le'u ste gnyis pa'o //    // de nas dbang chen rgyal po la //
NG0604:83: gsung gi rdo rjes 'di skad zhus //
NG0604:84: e ma ho dbang gi rgyal po lags //
NG0604:85: dbang mchog rgyal po lta ba ji ltar lags //
NG0604:86: de skad gsol ba gsan nas kyang *//
NG0604:87: dbang chen rgyal pos bka' stsal pa //
NG0604:88: nyon cig 'dus pa'i tshogs rnams nyon //
NG0604:89: rta mchog rgyal po'i lta ba ni //
NG0604:91: ye nas ma bcos chos kyi sku //
NG0604:92: rta mgrin rgyal por ye nas gnas //
NG0604:93: skye 'gag gnyis kyi mtha' las grol //
NG0604:94: ma spangs mtha' bral gzung 'dzin med //
NG0604:95: ye nas rang byung ye shes la //
NG0604:96: mtshan med spros bral ye sangs rgyas //
NG0604:97: rang la gnas pas gzhan na med //
NG0604:98: bltas pas mthong ba ma yin te //
NG0604:99: rang rig rta mgrin lhun gyis grub //
NG0604:100: ma btsal bzhag pas rta mchog mthong *//
NG0604:101: mthong ba tsam gyis yang sangs rgyas //
NG0604:102: gzhan nas lta med rang las mthong *//
NG0604:103: rta mchog rgyal po'i lta bar yin //
NG0604:105: lta ba'i le'u ste gsum pa'o //
NG0604:106: de nas rta mchog sgom pa gsungs //
NG0604:107: dbang chen rta mchog sgom 'dod na //
NG0604:108: lus ni ma bcos bde ba che //
NG0604:109: rta mgrin sku ru gsal stong *//
NG0604:110: gsal stong gnyis med sgom pa'i mchog / ngag ni
NG0604:111: rang byung sngags kyi sgra / sgra ru grags pas
NG0604:112: ngo bos stong *// grag stong gnyis med sgom pa'i mchog / sems ni ma bcos bde ba che //
NG0604:113: gsal la ma 'gags ngo bo stong *//
NG0604:114: bde stong gnyis med sgom pa'i mchog / rnam rtog chos nyid ngang du ni //
NG0604:115: dug lnga rang sar rjes med grol //
NG0604:116: ma spangs mtha' bral gzung 'dzin med //
NG0604:117: rig pa rang byung rta mgrin yin //
NG0604:118: ye nas ma bsgrubs rang la gnas //
NG0604:119: bsgoms dang ma bsgoms gnyis med na //
NG0604:120: thob med don la rtsol sgrub med //
NG0604:121: ri dgas smig rgyu snyeg pa 'dra //
NG0604:122: bsgrub pas grub par mi 'gyur ro //
NG0604:123: rang la bzhag nas gzhan la btsal //
NG0604:126: bsgom pa bstan pa'i le'u bzhi pa'o //    // de nas rta mchog spyod pa gsungs //
NG0604:127: rta mgrin rgyal po'i spyod pa ni //
NG0604:128: chos sku skye med ngang nyid nas //
NG0604:129: log lta zhi bas mi 'dul ba //
NG0604:130: longs sku thugs rje chen po yis //
NG0604:131: khro bo rta mchog rgyal por sprul //
NG0604:132: mkha' ltar khyab pa'i thugs rje yis //
NG0604:133: 'khor ba'i sdug bsngal nyon mongs rnams //
NG0604:134: thams cad ma lus 'joms pa mdzad //
NG0604:135: rnam rtog zung du 'jil bar mdzad //
NG0604:136: 'di ltar snang ba'i chos rnams la //
NG0604:137: 'dzin chags med par rang bzhin gsal //
NG0604:138: snang tsam nyid na ngo bo stong *//
NG0604:139: snang stong gnyis med rang grol spyod //
NG0604:140: rnam rtog dug lnga gang skyes pa //
NG0604:141: 'dzin med zhen med rang grol la //
NG0604:144: chos nyid rang sangs ngang du spyod //
NG0604:145: 'khor ba mi spong rang grol la //
NG0604:146: mya ngan 'das pa mi sgrub pa //
NG0604:147: 'khor ba rang bzhin med ces na //
NG0604:148: mya 'das sangs rgyas de ltar ro //
NG0604:149: khyad par rta mgrin spyod pa ni //
NG0604:150: khams gsum thams cad dbang bsdus nas //
NG0604:151: thams cad rgyal ba'i zhing du spyod //
NG0604:152: srid gsum thams cad zil gyis mnan //
NG0604:153: dregs pa tshar gcod las khol spyod /  rgyud drug 'khor ba rtsad bcad nas //
NG0604:154: thams cad byang chub lam la spyod //
NG0604:156: spyod pa bstan pa'i le'u ste lnga pa'o ///
NG0604:157: / de nas 'bras bu bsgrub pa gsungs //
NG0604:158: chos dbyings skye med spros dang bral //
NG0604:159: skye med don de brjod nus min //
NG0604:160: brjod med mtha' dang bral ba ni //
NG0604:161: chos sku rte mgrin zhes su brjod //
NG0604:162: thugs rje'i rang bzhin ma 'gags pas //
NG0604:164: thugs rje chen po thugs khros nas //
NG0604:165: rta mgrin khro bo'i skur bstan pa //
NG0604:166: longs spyod rdzogs sku'i rta mgrin yin //
NG0604:167: dregs pa bdud dpung gzhom pa'i phyir //
NG0604:168: sku mdog phyag mtshan cha lugs rnams //
NG0604:169: mi mthun so so grangs las 'das //
NG0604:170: gang la gang gis 'dul ba dang *//
NG0604:171: ci la cis 'dul gnyen por sprul //
NG0604:172: sprul pa sku yi rta mgrin yin //
NG0604:173: khyad par rta mgrin sgrub tu med //
NG0604:174: sems nyid ye nas rta mgrin la //
NG0604:175: skye med brjod med spros dang bral //
NG0604:176: gzugs dang kha dog mtshan ma med //
NG0604:177: chos sku rta mgrin ye nas grub //
NG0604:178: sems nyid ma 'gags rang byung la //
NG0604:179: dug lnga ye shes lnga ru shar //
NG0604:180: rnam rtog chos nyid ngang du grol //
NG0604:181: chod nyid longs spyod rgyun chad med //
NG0604:182: longs sku rta mgrin ye nas grub //
NG0604:183: phyi dang dngos por cir yang snang *//
NG0604:184: rang snang ngo bo rang sar grol //
NG0604:185: rgyud drug skye 'gro thams cad kyang *//
NG0604:186: rta mgrin sku de snang stong yin //
NG0604:187: sgra ru grags pa thams cad kyang *//
NG0604:188: rta mgrin gsung degrag stong yin //
NG0604:189: sems kyi dran rtogs thams cad kyang *//
NG0604:190: rta mgrin thugs de bde stong yin //
NG0604:191: thams cad sprul sku'i rta mgrin yin //
NG0604:193: 'bras bu'i le'u ste drug pa'o //    // rta mgrin dregs pa tshar gcod kyi rgyud las //
NG0604:194: lta sgom spyod pa 'bras bu'i skabs te dang po'o //     // de nas dbang mchog rgyal po la //
NG0604:195: gsung gi rdo rje 'di skad zhus //
NG0604:196: e ma ho dbang mchog rgyal po che //
NG0604:197: rta mgrin bsnyen pa ji ltar bya //
NG0604:198: dpa' bos rgyas par bshad du gsol //
NG0604:199: de skad gsol ba gsan nas kyang *//
NG0604:200: dbang chen rgyal pos bka' stsal pa //
NG0604:202: bsnyen pa la ni rnam pa gnyis //
NG0604:203: zhi ba dang ni khro bo'o //
NG0604:204: dang po zhi ba'i bsnyen pa ni //
NG0604:205: yid 'ong dben pa'i gnas su ni *//
NG0604:206: man+dal mchod pa bshams nas su //
NG0604:207: rten dang sku gzugs bkram byas la //
NG0604:208: gdong dang kha lag bkrus byas la //
NG0604:211: dang po byang chub sems bskyed la //
NG0604:212: bla med dkon mchog skyabs song la //
NG0604:213: bla ma sangs rgyas la sogs te //
NG0604:214: thugs rje chen po'i lha tshogs rnams //
NG0604:215: sbyan drangs bzhugs gsol phyag 'tshal mchod //
NG0604:216: sdig bshags rjes su yi rangs 'bul //
NG0604:217: chos kyi 'khor lo bskor bar bskul //
NG0604:218: mya ngan mi 'da' gsol ba gdab //
NG0604:219: dge ba byang chub don du bsngo //
NG0604:220: bdag gzhan byang chub thob par smon //
NG0604:221: de ltar bsod nams tshogs bsags nas //
NG0604:222: ye shes tshogs bsags sems bskyed bya //
NG0604:223: de nas ting nge 'dzin la 'jug / stong nyid spros bral de bzhin nyid //
NG0604:224: tshad med bzhi ldan kun tu snang *//
NG0604:225: ye shes sems dpa' tshogs nang rgyu //
NG0604:226: hu~m las ye she sa gzhal yas khang *//
NG0604:228: dbus gnas pad+ma 'dab bzhis bteg / phyi rol pad+ma 'dab drug mdzes //
NG0604:229: bar khyams sgo bzhi rgyan gyis mdzes //
NG0604:230: khor yug rdo rje ra ba la //
NG0604:231: ye shes me ri rab 'bar cing *//
NG0604:232: phyi rim byang chub shing gis mdzes //
NG0604:233: de dbus nyi zla pad+ma'i gdan //
NG0604:234: de dbus rgyu yis sems dpa' las //
NG0604:235: spro bsdu'i sbyor ba byas pa las //
NG0604:236: thugs rje chen po'i sku ru gyur //
NG0604:237: zhal gcig phyag bzhi sku mdog dkar //
NG0604:238: 'dzum byas spyan dmar mdzes pa'i zhal //
NG0604:239: phyag gnyis thugs khar thal mo sbyar //
NG0604:242: rin po che yi rgyan gyis brgyan //
NG0604:243: pad+ma zla ba'i gdan la bzhugs //
NG0604:244: thugs kar ye shes sems dpa' bzhugs //
NG0604:245: rigs kyi bdag pos dbu la brgyan //
NG0604:246: snang la rang bzhin med pa bsgom //
NG0604:247: de nas yi ge drug ma yum //
NG0604:248: zhal gcig phyag gnyis gtso dang thun //
NG0604:249: g.yas su nor bu 'dzin pa dkar //
NG0604:250: zhal gcig phyag gnyis nor bu 'dzin //
NG0604:251: g.yon du rig sngags 'dzin ma dkar //
NG0604:252: zhal gcig phyag gnyis shel 'phreng bsnams //
NG0604:253: rin po che yi rgyan gyis brgyan //
NG0604:254: yum sras yab la 'dud tshul bskyed //
NG0604:255: de nas 'khor gyi lha bskyed pa //
NG0604:256: phyi rol pad+ma'i gdan stengs su //
NG0604:257: yab kyi thugs kha'i hri 'phros pas //
NG0604:258: 'khor du rgyal ba rigs drug bskyed //
NG0604:259: spyan ras gzigs dbang pad+ma dkar //
NG0604:260: rdo rje sems dpa' rdo rje dkar //
NG0604:261: rnam par snang mdzad 'khor lo dkar //
NG0604:262: rin chen 'byung ldan rin chen ser //
NG0604:263: snang ba mtha' yas pad+ma dmar //
NG0604:264: don grub ljang khu rgya gram ljang *//
NG0604:265: pha rol phyin drug yum gyi tshul //
NG0604:266: shes rab bsam gtan brtson 'grus dang *//
NG0604:267: sbyin pa tshul khrims bzod pa rnams //
NG0604:268: gtso bo'i sku mdog phyag mtshan 'dzin / dbyings dang ye shes yab dang sbyor //
NG0604:269: sgo bzhi sprul sku thub pa drug / shar sgor brgya byin pi wang dkar //
NG0604:272: lho sgor shag thub gseg shang bar //
NG0604:273: shakya seng ge po ti bsnams //
NG0604:274: nub sgo nam mkha' mdzod dmar rin chen sgrom //
NG0604:275: byang sgor chos rgyal me chu gnag / snang la rang bzhin med par sgom //
NG0604:276: sku gsung thugs su byin gyis brlabs //
NG0604:277: rigs lnga ye shes dkyil 'khor dbang bskur bya //
NG0604:278: de nas ye shes dkyil 'khor bsgrub //
NG0604:279: rang bzhin gnas nas spyan drangs pa //
NG0604:280: bzhugs su gsol zhing phyag 'tshal mchod //
NG0604:281: bstod cing 'phrin las bcol ba bya //
NG0604:282: tshogs la sogs pas 'byor tshogs mchod //
NG0604:283: de nas bsnyen bsgrub dbul ba ni //
NG0604:284: thugs rje chen po'i thugs kha ru //
NG0604:285: zla dkyil hrih la sngags kyis bskor //
NG0604:287: 'khor gyi lha rnams thugs ka nas //
NG0604:288: sngags kyi 'phreng ba gnas pa la //
NG0604:290: phyogs bcu'i sangs rgyas byang chub sems //
NG0604:293: khams gsum sems can sgrib pa sbyang *//
NG0604:294: thugs rje'i chen po'i sku ru gyur //
NG0604:295: slar 'dus rang gi sgrib pa dag / sku gsung thugs kyi dngos grub thob //
NG0604:296: de ltar spro bsdu'i ting nge 'dzin gyis //
NG0604:297: ye shes lha la bsnyen pa 'bul //
NG0604:298: thun mtshams lha la mchod pa 'bul //
NG0604:299: chos skyong rnams la gtor ma 'bul /
NG0604:301: ye shes semasas dpa' gshegs su gsol //
NG0604:302: dam tshig sems dpa' gtso la bsdu //
NG0604:303: de yang thugs ka'i hri la bsda //
NG0604:304: hri yang rims kyis thig ler bsdu //
NG0604:305: thig le mi dmigs chos kyi dbyings //
NG0604:306: spros pa med pa'i ngang la bzhag / thun bzhi thun drug nyams su blangs //
NG0604:307: thun gyi dang po bskyed rim bya //
NG0604:308: thun gyi tham bsdu gshegs bya //
NG0604:309: de la dus kyi bsnyen pa ni //
NG0604:310: zhag grangs zla grangs lo la sogs //
NG0604:311: rab 'bring tha mar sbyar te sgrub //
NG0604:312: grangs kyi bsnyen pa 'bum dang ni //
NG0604:313: bye ba sa ya gang 'grub sgrub //
NG0604:314: rtags ni bsnyen pa zhal mthong dang *//
NG0604:315: 'od dang sgra dang lung ston dang *//
NG0604:316: nad gdon sel dang bar chad sol //
NG0604:317: mchog dang thun mong dngos grub 'byung *//
NG0604:318: de ltar zhe ba'i bsnyen pa yis //
NG0604:319: zhi ba thugs rje chen po grub par sgrub //
NG0604:320: dngos grub myur du thob par 'gyur //
NG0604:321: sangs rgyas byang chub the tshom med //
NG0604:323: zhi ba'i bsnyen pa'i le'u ste bdun pa'o ///
NG0604:324: / rta mgrin dregs pa tshar gcod kyi rgyud las //
NG0604:325: zhi ba'i bsnyen pa'i skabs te gnyis pa'o ///
NG0604:326: / de nas yang dag bshad bya ba //
NG0604:327: khro bo'i bsnyen pa bstan pa ni //
NG0604:328: dang po dben pa'i gnas su ni //
NG0604:329: man+da la phyi nang mchod pa bshams //
NG0604:330: nub tu kha gahad gos dmar bgo //
NG0604:331: pad+ma ra ga'i phreng ba'i bgrang *//
NG0604:332: bde ba'i rtan la 'dug nas su //
NG0604:333: skad cig stong pa'i ngang las ni //
NG0604:336: rta skad 'don cing mtshams bcad la //
NG0604:337: bar chad bgegs rnams bskrad par bya //
NG0604:338: sngon 'gro yan lag bcu pa bya //
NG0604:339: gtor ma rak+ta bdud rtsi rnams //
NG0604:340: mchod rdzas byin gyis brlab par bya //
NG0604:341: sngon du 'gro ba'i las rdzogs nas //
NG0604:342: dam tshig dkyil 'khor bskyed pa ni //
NG0604:343: de bzhin nyid kyi ting nge 'dzin //
NG0604:344: ma bcos spros med byang chub dang *//
NG0604:345: kun tu snang gi ting nge 'dzin //
NG0604:346: ma rtogs sems can snying rje bskyed //
NG0604:347: bskyed pa rgyu yi ting nge 'dzin //
NG0604:348: rang sems ye shes sems dpar gsal //
NG0604:349: rang lus nang gi 'byung ba dang *//
NG0604:350: snod bcud 'byung ba phyi spyad phyir //
NG0604:351: nam mkha' rlung dang chu dang sa //
NG0604:352: ri rab dang ni ma la sogs //
NG0604:353: sems dang dbugs dang sha dang khrag / drod dang rus pa sbyar ba'i phyir //
NG0604:354: 'byung ba rim brtsegs bskyed par bya //
NG0604:355: de nas b+h+rum las gzhal yas khang *//
NG0604:356: dregs pa gdug pa 'dul ba'i phyir //
NG0604:357: gzhal yas khang gi rtsigs pa dang *//
NG0604:358: ka gdung gral bkram skar khung bstod //
NG0604:359: phyogs skyong bcu yi rtsig rmang la //
NG0604:360: lha chen brgyad kyi rtsig pa la //
NG0604:361: klu chen brgyad kyi gdung ma bri //
NG0604:362: rgyal chen zhi yi ka ba la //
NG0604:363: lha chen brgyad po bad du bor //
NG0604:364: rgyu skar rnams kyis gral krab bya //
NG0604:365: nyi zla gnyis kyi skar khung stod //
NG0604:366: pho brang 'khor lo rtsibs bzhi la //
NG0604:367: phyi rol 'khor lo rtsibs drug mdzes //
NG0604:368: gru chad bar khyams sgo bzhir ldan //
NG0604:369: rdo rje ra ba me ri 'bar //
NG0604:370: de dbus nyi zla pad+ma gdan //
NG0604:371: 'khor lo'i rtsibs la dregs pa'i gdan //
NG0604:372: sgo bzhi 'gro ba rigs drug gdan //
